Class ConfigurationManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • cz.apolicky.summercampapp.ConfigurationManager

  • public class ConfigurationManager
extends java.lang.Object
    A class that provides access to fields with information saved in a json file. Returns values as String, Int, IntArray, ...
